{"tid":1795494,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[N_BXX又..]疑賓館內拍針昏迷 兩內地男一死一傷","createTime":"2019-12-24T03:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T03:07:56.000Z","uid":8968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b8f03b9f130ccf6eb9ca739fa94c627197fb8d52","tid":1795494,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T03:06:17.000Z","msg":"深水埗大南街271號一間<span style=\"color: red;\">賓</span>館，晚上8時許，職員發現一房間客人逾時未退房，拍門無反應，於是用後備匙開門查看，赫見兩名內地男租客昏迷不醒，慌忙報案。警員及救護員接報到場，將兩名男子送往明愛醫院搶救，其中一人不治，另一人則仍在搶救。<br />\n警員在現場發現<span style=\"color: red;\">兩枝針筒</span>及錫紙，不排除兩人為癮君子，疑吸食過量毒品出事，正就事件展開調查，案件初步並無可疑，男死者姓趙45歲，另一姓梁40歲內地男子留醫治理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe5d613d98d32e4790bcc8c1ce392603b1f84946","tid":1795494,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T03:07:34.000Z","msg":"請使用不推文功能 以降低上熱門分數"},{"pid":"0d355ff8147313298f248b7f20803354a6b4e355","tid":1795494,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe5d613d98d32e4790bcc8c1ce392603b1f84946","tid":1795494,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T03:07:34.000Z","msg":"請使用不推文功能 以降低上熱門分數"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T03:07:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}